responseText: The epigrah is Ancient Vaelune, that much is clear.  Many words can be ambiguous, unlike modern Kaelar Common.  I will translate the ones I know here on this page.  I am sure Qatakijal will find it useful.  Thank you, my friend, for helping us uncover a part of our history.  May you find fortune in your travels.
name: DD_SQ_0012_VaeluneScholar4_4_Response
